!   neighbor of X in the direction of Y. The neighbors of zero (of either 
!   sign) are both nonzero. IEEE_OVERFLOW is signaled when X is finite but 
!   IEEE_NEXT_AFTER(X,Y) is infinite; IEEE_UNDERFLOW is signaled when 
